data.description: Welcome home to a stunning two-story in Lakeshore! This beautiful residence offers a perfect blend of modern updates and rustic charm. Enjoy an open floor plan with high ceilings, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere in the living area. The well-appointed updates include luxurious LVP flooring and stunning rustic light fixtures, adding a touch of elegance to the home. The kitchen boasts neutral accents, stainless appliances, gas cooking, a newer dishwasher, and microwave, making it a chef's dream. A dedicated home office, provides a peaceful and productive environment. Upstairs, you'll find a fantastic game room. The covered rear patio and large backyard is an ideal spot for relaxation and hosting outdoor gatherings. Desirable 4-car tandem garage. As part of the Lakeshore community, you'll have access to a refreshing pool, perfect for those hot summer days. Community Pool and Elementary school conveniently located nearby ensuring a convenient and family-friendly lifestyle.
